國藉或居住國家申請簽證。任何人士合法在香港或澳門停留可在香港申請簽證。不過，申請人除了考慮到方便或原居地延遲安排預約，更應該考慮在有緊密聯係的領事轄區內申請。<br />\n<br />\n我們不能保證向你簽發簽證，也不能保證處理時間。如申請遭拒，所繳付的申請費恕不獲退還。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ustraveldocs.com/hk_zh/hk-gen-faq.asp#qlistgen5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ustraveldocs.com%2Fhk_zh%2Fhk-gen-faq.asp%23qlistgen5&d=btCVXQQjrXwPBq5llfxgHwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=bf42c35f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ustraveldocs.com/hk_zh/hk-gen-faq.asp#qlistgen5</a>"},{"pid":"226a2fdbcfb4bd8102d4aac3997475f03b37294b","tid":544670,"uid":51744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4db3f2342b8131f88dd059262a7364bf3ed698b2","tid":544670,"uid":91793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T19:35:14.000Z","msg":"同問 如果美國簽証5月完 想再延長<br />\n係美國整唔整到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T21:01:43.000Z","msg":"問 10. 如何延長我的簽證？<br />\n不論任何簽證類別，都無法延長有效期。你必須申請新簽證。<br />\n<br />\n既然係重新申請，需要返回原居地申請。"},{"pid":"b4f52179c1fc7942ccc4ae641a6f1e9d74518531","tid":544670,"uid":61630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc1e5df11954e41d8b2ca4cf77dc55ccf191496b","tid":544670,"uid":51744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T20:57:23.000Z","msg":"問 5 我是第三國家國民居住於香港或澳門，我可以在香港申請非移民簽證嗎？<br />\n申請人一般建議在自己國藉或居住國家申請簽證。任何人士合法在香港或澳門停留可在香港申請簽證。不過，申請人除了考慮到方便或原居地延遲安排預約，更應該考慮在有緊密聯係的領事轄區內申請。<br />\n<br />\n我們不能保證向你簽發簽證，也不能保證處理時間。如申請遭拒，所繳付的申請費恕不獲退還。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ustraveldocs.com/hk_zh/hk-gen-faq.asp#qlistgen5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ustraveldocs.com%2Fhk_zh%2Fhk-gen-faq.asp%23qlistgen5&d=btCVXQQjrXwPBq5llfxgHwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=bf42c35f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ustraveldocs.com/hk_zh/hk-gen-faq.asp#qlistgen5</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-